claims:
11.一种锂基电池，其包括：11. A lithium-based battery comprising:


         负极；negative electrode;


         包括活性物质的正极；a positive electrode comprising an active material;


         位于负极和正极之间的隔膜，所述隔膜包括：A separator located between the negative and positive electrodes, the separator comprising:


         具有相对表面的多孔聚合物膜，所述相对表面之一面对正极；a porous polymer membrane having opposing surfaces, one of which faces the positive electrode;


         在相对表面所述之一上形成的多孔碳涂层；和a porous carbon coating formed on said one of the opposing surfaces; and


         引入该多孔碳涂层、多孔聚合物膜、或多孔碳涂层和多孔聚合物膜两者中的聚阳离子材料；和a polycation material incorporated into the porous carbon coating, porous polymer membrane, or both the porous carbon coating and porous polymer membrane; and


         浸泡各正极、负极、和隔膜的电解质溶液。The electrolytic solution of each positive electrode, negative electrode, and separator is soaked.
